Package: libdist-zilla-plugin-changelogfromgit-debian-sequential-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}, lsb-release, libdist-zilla-perl,
 libdatetime-format-mail-perl, dh-make-perl, libdist-zilla-plugin-changelogfromgit-perl, libdpkg-perl
Description: Add changelog entries into debain/changelog
 ChangelogFromGit::Debian::Sequential extends
 Dist::Zilla::Plugin::ChangelogFromGit to create/update Debian changelog. It
 does not recreate changelog every time like
 Dist::Zilla::Plugin::ChangelogFromGit::Debian.
